commit.message: Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/rauroll/coffee-sloth-ios
update the project for ios 10.1 and swift 3
Create README.md
Made changes to the horizontal bar -obstacle's positioning
Coffees now spawn in strings
Reimplemented sloth controls, re-scaled some game objects
adds images
Coffees are now worth ten points, changed the section weights.
Added a simple main menu and a proper overlay for the gameover state.
Added coffeebar and score to overlay.
Moved Section class form utilities to sections.
Added owl, refactored the audio player to use singleton design pattern
Added some sounds to the game!
Some contact handling added.
Added features to the section manager and added a couple sections.
Added a generic queue struct, created dummies for section manager and the section base class
Added utilities and some sloth movements
Added the sloth and some other boilerplate code
Initial commit, project started and background added.
Initial Commit
